# --- Local DB schema sync artifacts ---
# Generated schema snapshots and local sync metadata.
# These files may contain server/database identifiers or full schema details.
# Do not commit these files. Use governed migration files and sanitized examples instead.
db/memory.lock.json
db/schema.json
db/schema.sql
db/tables.md
db/schema_snapshots/

# ⚠️ IMPORTANT (schema / migrations policy):
# Root-level db/schema.sql is a generated local schema snapshot and is ignored (see above).
# Governed migration SQL files should live under governed migration paths (e.g. db/migrations/),
# not as root-level generated snapshot files. The db/migrations/ tree remains version-controlled — do not ignore it.

